
Overview of noun danger

The noun danger has 4 senses (first 4 from tagged texts)
                                         
1. (18) danger -- (the condition of being susceptible to harm or injury; "you are in no danger"; "there was widespread danger of disease")
2. (8) risk, peril, danger -- (a venture undertaken without regard to possible loss or injury; "he saw the rewards but not the risks of crime"; "there was a danger he would do the wrong thing")
3. (6) danger -- (a cause of pain or injury or loss; "he feared the dangers of traveling by air")
4. (1) danger -- (a dangerous place; "He moved out of danger")
